title: CT Fernando
description:
This is a great collection of songs from C.T. Fernando. It is ripped from a CD.
 
However, unlike the modern CD's this contains the ORIGINAL recordings that could be found on the original gramophone recordings.

The only reason I am uploading this is because all the modern CD versions of his hits have done the original musicians a great disservice with poor use of digital drums and adding extra melodies or removing original material from the song.

I will be looking to add some other songs later on.

ENJOY!
